# Title

MAL Tournament

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Short Description

An app to determine scores for your completed anime list on myanimelist.net

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Full Description

This app allows you to play rating tournaments using your list of completed anime series from
myanimelist.net. Different series will be pitted against each other in different styles of rating contests
and the scores of the shows will be adjusted accordingly.

You will have to enter your username and password for myanimelist.net. This information will not be
stored locally on your device nor will it be used for anything other than authenticating your device
with the myanimelist.net servers.

A privacy statement can be read at
http://gitlab.namibsun.net/namboy94/mal-tournament/raw/master/mal-tournament-android/playstore/privacy_statement.

We also offer separate apk builds on our github release page:
https://github.com/namboy94/mal-tournament/releases

It also offers a graphical Java program for desktop operating systems that has roughly the same feature set as
the android app

This app is completely open source under the GPLv3 license. Check out the source code for this project at its
github page: https://github.com/namboy94/mal-tournament

or if you want to contribute, join us on our privately hosted gitlab instance:
http://gitlab.namibsun.net/namboy94/mal-tournament



